thi giả - 凡讀我詩者</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-Thai-th%E1%BA%A1ch-l%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-h%E1%BA%ADu-quan-b%E1%BB%99c-b%E1%BB%91/poem-Vqow27pdQlBUwaSkG3-PNQ">Thiên Thai thạch lương hậu quan bộc bố - 天台石梁雨後觀瀑布</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-zQyjfkM-l-eVSsp11IFYtg">Nguỵ Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/Th%C3%B4i-t%C3%B4-h%C3%A0nh/poem-gmB1n6my6IUHsIlOzc-dWQ">Thôi tô hành - 催租行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/author-ppK7YKfOyDZw9vIHLHbJVA">Phạm Thành Đại</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%E1%BB%AD-Th%C3%A0nh/T%C3%ADch-xu%C3%A2n/poem-hwm8DGsBn00rYiD6kH_Fwg">Tích xuân - 惜春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%E1%BB%AD-Th%C3%A0nh/author-HYGFT6wTz4aNfPlamWDBRw">Nguyễn Tử Thành</a>)<br></div>	</div>
